Jun 27, 2022 Chopped the second mortice for the bottom back bar.
Jun 28, 2022 Drilled the holes in the side frame for the back bar bolts by hand. Marked the position of the longitudinal holes in the back bar. Brought the drill press in and set it up and drilled the holes. Took the drill back outside again.  
Jun 29, 2022 Cut the nut mortices and fitted the bottom back bar.
Jun 30, 2022 Reviewed state of Steve's mobile and started looking for some pieces to make the remaining planets and moons.
Jul 2,  2022 Cut out a new version of Saturn for Steve's mobile. Also Neptune, but that broke when trilling it for the hanging thread. Added threads to the sun, mercury, Venus, Jupiter and Saturn. Made a new drill to make the holes, from a fine needle (24thou or thereabouts).
