Sep 23, 2022 Planed the rest of the face-end of the segments of the wheel. Measured the length, adjusted the 2 smallest outliers by taking a little off the inner face, then marked them all to the same length. 
Sep 24, 2022 Planed all 12 segments to length. Just cut to the marked line. Some error may have crept in, it looks like one or two are not perfectly square between the ends and the face side. Adjusting that will be next, hopefully without messing up the length. I think they really need to match in length.
