Jan 27, 2023 Cut the inner curve and cleaned it all up. Cut the second piece, but managed to break it cleaning up the inner curve. Will make it again, It needs to be strong.
Jan 28, 2023 Made a replacement top rib.
Jan 29, 2023 Glued in the top binding strips and fitted the ribs. Top ribs are too deeply curved. Not sure if it was deliberate, but the curve of the end pieces is less than on the plans so the top rib ship stands too high. Need to make them again. Started looking for stock.
