May 1,  2023 Cut the second bar to the correct width and cut the third bar.
May 2,  2023 Cut the front piece to width. Cleaned up all the face sides and edges of the treadle pieces. Cleaned up the opposite sides of the 3 bars and the front piece
May 3,  2023 Finished off preparing the back and bottom of the back piece of the treadle. Marked out all the mortice and tenon joints.
