Dec 3, 2025 Cleaning continues. Been doing little else since we got home. Was that a week ago? Starting to plan how to rearrange tool storage. Although the carpenters tool chest is excellent for accessibility, its not good for mobility. If the floods come there is no way I can carry it upstairs. It is also very much all in one. It might make more sense to have multiple smaller toolboxes for specific purposes. First one would be the lathe toolbox for chucks and turning tools, second would be for flute drills and reamers. Not sure how to divide up the rest. There would need to be a general purpose toolbox I think. Maybe one for drilling holes and one for basic joinery (saws, marking guages and squares). One for metalwork with files and hacksaws.
